                     <interp inst="t18220109-134-victim1179" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , by banns, on the <rs id="t18220109-134-cd717" type="crimeDate">28th of May, 1810</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220109-134-off716 t18220109-134-cd717"></join>; it is witnessed by 
